Step-by-Step Instructions

1. Go to Spring Initializr
Open https://start.spring.io/

2. Fill project details
Group: com.cognizant
Artifact: spring-learn
Name: spring-learn (auto-filled)

Dependencies:
Select Spring Web
Select Spring Boot DevTools

3. Download and Extract
Click Generate
A zip file will download
Extract the zip file to your Eclipse workspace folder

4. Import to Eclipse
Go to Eclipse > File > Import
Select Maven > Existing Maven Projects
Click Browse, choose the extracted spring-learn folder
Click Finish

5. Run the Project
Right-click on SpringLearnApplication.java

Choose Run As > Java Application
